#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-kapplication; is an editor for Sieve scripts used for email filtering "
"on a mail server."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication; je urejevalnik za skripte Sieve, ki se uporabljajo za "
"filtriranje elektronske pošte na poštnem strežniku."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sieve"
msgstr "Sieve"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-kapplication; is an editor for <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Sieve_(mail_filtering_language)\">Sieve</ulink> scripts used for email "
"filtering on a mail server."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication; je urejevalnik <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/Sieve_(mail_filtering_language)\">Sieve</ulink> skriptov, ki se "
"uporabljajo za filtriranje e-pošte na poštnem strežniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &i18n-kapplication;"
msgstr "Uporaba &i18n-kapplication;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "&i18n-kapplication; provides a &GUI; to perform these tasks:"
msgstr "&i18n-kapplication; ponuja &GUI; za opravljanje teh nalog:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manage your Sieve servers"
msgstr "Upravljajte svoje strežnike Sieve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Upload, import and deactivate scripts, refresh the list with scripts"
msgstr "Naložite, uvozite in deaktivirajte skripte, osvežite seznam s skripti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create and edit Sieve scripts"
msgstr "Ustvarite in uredite Sieve skripte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and share scripts"
msgstr "Uvozite in delite skripte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check the script syntax, autogenerate and debug scripts"
msgstr ""
"Preverite sintakso skripta, samodejno ustvarite skripte in skripte za "
"odpravljanje napak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&i18n-kapplication; can be used independent from Akonadi or &kmail;, you "
"only need a mail server with support for Sieve scripts."
msgstr ""
"&i18n-kapplication; lahko uporabljate neodvisno od Akonadija ali &kmail;a, "
"potrebujete samo poštni strežnik s podporo za Sieve skripte."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "In a &plasma-desktop; the passwords are stored in &kwallet5;"
msgstr "V namizju &plasma-desktop; so gesla shranjena v &kwallet5;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "First Start"
msgstr "Prvi začetek"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the first start of &i18n-kapplication; the server configuration dialog is "
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Ob prvem zagonu &i18n-kapplication; se prikaže pogovorno okno za "
"konfiguracijo strežnika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Server Configuration</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracija strežnika</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Server Configuration</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracija strežnika</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "In this dialog you can add, modify and remove your mails servers."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko dodate, spremenite in odstranite svoje poštne "
"strežnike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Later you can use <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add "
"Server</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or the configuration dialog for these "
"tasks."
msgstr ""
"Kasneje lahko za ta opravila uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj strežnik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the next start &i18n-kapplication; automatically fetches all available "
"scripts from the servers."
msgstr ""
"Ob naslednjem zagonu &i18n-kapplication; samodejno pridobi vse razpoložljive "
"skripte s strežnikov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Script Editing</title>"
msgstr "<title>Urejanje skripta</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "The editor supports autocompletion and syntax highlighting."
msgstr "Urejevalnik podpira samodokončanje in označevanje sintakse."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Script Editing</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Urejanje skripta</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Script Editing</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Urejanje skripta</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Tools"
msgstr "Orodja za skripte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actions in the <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> menu enable you to check the "
"syntax of your scripts, autogenerate and debug scripts."
msgstr ""
"Dejanja v meniju <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> vam omogočajo, da preverite "
"sintakso svojih skriptov, samodejno ustvarite in razhroščite skripte."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Autogenerate scripts</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Samodejno ustvari skripte</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Autogenerate scripts</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Samodejno ustvari skripte</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Integrated Help</title>"
msgstr "<title>Integrirana pomoč</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the integrated help support and click with the &RMB; on a "
"keyword of the Sieve language. Then the corresponding section of the "
"documentation is downloaded from the Internet and displayed in the "
"<guilabel>Help</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite lahko integrirano podporo za pomoč in kliknite z desnim klikom na "
"ključno besedo jezika Sieve. Nato se ustrezen razdelek dokumentacije prenese "
"z interneta in prikaže na zavihku <guilabel>Pomoč</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Integrated Help</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Integrirana pomoč</screeninfo>"

